name: Woman & Rose
description:
woman and rose

so the story this time when I was chill at the table with a glass of coffee.

I imagine a woman and a rose, yes in the object that I drew this time, a rose is a beautiful but cruel flower, has a fragrant fragrance, a glamorous color but has a sharp stem, just like a beautiful woman, glamorous, very sharp with thorns, in love and women we should hold roses, there is a price to be paid for its beauty. by hellotitto
